These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-1-1::.
There 7 different types of food: apple, plum, tomato, potato, pomegranate, eggplant, peach
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: basketball, tennis, badminton, cycling, skateboarding, climbing, ice-hockey
The people use 7 different means of transport: car, scooter, boat, bike, quad-bike, ship, roller
 1. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person eating plum##1
 5. the person eating peach is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
 6. the person eating tomato is the person driving the boat##1
 7. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 8. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 9. the person driving the boat is the person who's sport is badminton##1
10. the person driving the bike is the person eating pomegranate##1
11. the person eating apple is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
12. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
13. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
14. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
15. the person eating plum is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |     3     |     4     |      5       |     6      |     7      |
| Food        | potato | tomato     | eggplant | plum | apple      | peach | pomegranate       |
| Sport       | tennis        | badminton   | basketball   | ice-hockey    | climbing | cycling    | skateboarding     |
| Transport   | car    | boat | roller       | ship     | scooter   | quad-bike     | bike |

