.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-1-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: juice, water, lemonade, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea, soy-milk
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: adventure, drama, martial-arts, time-travel, thriller, family, spy
7 different pets are kept: ferret, snake, pony, guinea-pig, goldfish, frog, rat
 1. the person drinking lemonade is the person watching time-travel movies##1
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
 3. the person watching thriller movies is the owner of the frog##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 5. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 8. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 9. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the person watching spy movies is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
11. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
12. the owner of the snake is the person drinking tea##1
13. the owner of the frog is the person drinking juice##1
14. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person drinking water##1
15. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
16. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |     4     |   5    |   6    |   7    |
| Beverage      | soy-milk  | juice     | hot-chocolate  | mirinda  | lemonade   | water | tea   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | thriller | spy | adventure | time-travel | family | drama |
| Pet           | pony    | frog   | guinea-pig  | rat    | goldfish | ferret   | snake    |

