7 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rabbit, bird, chinchilla, frog, rat, hamster
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: handball, baseball, swimming, parkour, ice-hockey, badminton, soccer
 1. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person eating onion##1
 2. the owner of the bird is the person who's sport is soccer##1
 3. the owner of the hamster is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 4. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1
 6. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating onion##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
11. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
12. the person eating onion is in the middle##1
13. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
14. the person eating lime is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
15. the person who's sport is parkour is in the middle##1
16. the owner of the hedgehog is the person eating garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
