 2. the fan of gospel is the architect##1
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 5. the architect is in the middle##1
 6. the fan of punk is on the left of the coach##1
 7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the accountant##1
 8. the fan of country is the mechanic##1
 9. the coach is on the left of the fan of rock##1
10. the fan of metal is on the right of the videographer##1
11. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the videographer##1
12. the electrician is on the left of the coach##1
13. the fan of country is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
14. the mechanic is on the left of the videographer##1
15. the person who's hobby is cooking is the electrician##1
16. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
