 1. the project-manager is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 2. the person eating pepper is on the right of the project-manager##1
 3. the freelancer is on the left of the librarian##1
 4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person eating onion##1
 6. the teacher is the person watching action movies##1
 7. the teacher is on the left of the videographer##1
 8. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1
 9. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the teacher##1
10. the person eating radish is the freelancer##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the freelancer##1
12. the person eating kiwi is in the middle##1
13. the person eating broccoli is the person watching thriller movies##1
14. the person watching action movies is the person eating peach##1
15. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
16. the designer is on the right of the person eating onion##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |     4     |      5      |      6      |     7      |
| Food          | onion    | pepper | peach  | kiwi | pomegranate | radish     | broccoli    |
| Job           | project-manager    | designer  | teacher | videographer | firefighter       | freelancer    | librarian |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | crime  | action      | comedy | horror      | disaster | thriller    |

